nger-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-singer-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>为了庆祝她的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-banks-15615-325201">Goddess</a> 》发行 10 周年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/banks">班克斯</a>宣布推出新的原声版本，并在英国和美国举办三场亲密的现场表演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/banks-serpentina-3196028">Banks –“Serpentina”：创新且富有弹性的重新推出，带有大胆的新声音</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手今天（9月5日）早些时候在Instagram上宣布了专辑和演出的消息，并分享门票将于当地时间周二（9月10日）上午10点开始发售——您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbanks-tickets%2Fartist%2F1892401" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买门票。</p><p>门票将于 9 月 9 日星期一开始预售，凡报名提前观看演出的粉丝均可<a href="https://laylo.com/hernameisbanks/vpSgO" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预售。</p><p>这位歌手在 10 年前的 2014 年 9 月 5 日发行了《Goddess》，但名为《Goddess Unplugged》的原声版本尚未发行——虽然她今天宣布了这张专辑，但尚未透露发行日期。</p><p>与此同时，她将要演出的演出将在她十年前推出《女神》时曾演出的三个场地举行。她将于10月21日在伦敦的Koko举行演出，然后于10月23日在洛杉矶的El Rey剧院举行一场演出，最后两天在纽约市的欧文广场举行了一场演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3791066" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791066" style="width: 1080px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791066" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-Admat-Goddess-10-Year-1080-x-1080.jpg" alt="银行旅行海报" width="1080" height="1080" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-Admat-Goddess-10-Year-1080-x-1080.jpg 1080w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-Admat-Goddess-10-Year-1080-x-1080-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-Admat-Goddess-10-Year-1080-x-1080-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-Admat-Goddess-10-Year-1080-x-1080-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-Admat-Goddess-10-Year-1080-x-1080-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Banks-Admat-Goddess-10-Year-1080-x-1080-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791066" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>Banks在Instagram上说：“今天是如此特殊的一天。这是我的首张专辑“女神”的十周年，我只是想花一秒钟跳到这里，告诉大家我对你有多感激，对我的意义 - 从一开始就一直与我在一起的每个人当然，那些沿途加入的人。我从内心深处爱你，我想为你们做一些特别的事情。”</p><p>她还告诉粉丝们要“敬请期待”下周的另一个重大公告，然后结束时说：“我爱大家，让我们他妈的一起庆祝。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_ip23NvgXN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,